/cvmfs/alice.cern.ch/bin/alienv enter VO_ALICE@AliDPG::v5-08-XX-15,VO_ALICE@AliPhysics::v5-08-13u-01-cookdedx-1

run number 257893 (LHC16k) is picked up for the test porpose.
A sample JDL is https://alimonitor.cern.ch/productions/9250/JDL.html
So, please copy 2 files from alien
/alice/sim/2016/LHC16j2a1/OCDB/257893/OCDBsim.root (335 MB)
/alice/sim/2016/LHC16j2a1/OCDB/257893/OCDBrec.root (335 MB)

To run full simulation, please do:
./dpgsim.sh --run 257893 --mode full --uid 1 --nevents 1 --generator PHOSPi0 --detector PHOS --simulation PHOS --reconstruction PHOS
